Class Pass

java.lang.Object
Pass
Direct Known Subclasses:
BusinessPass, EmployeePass, TouristPass
public class Pass
extends java.lang.Object
A Pass represents a person in the resort who has an id number, a name, a luxury rating, a certain number of credits, and a certain amount of journey points.
